name: PIMCO Managed Core Bond Pool
longDescription: The investment objective of the Fund is to achieve maximum total return, consistent with preservation of capital and prudent investment management. The Fund invests primarily in units of other mutual funds managed by PIMCO Canada, emphasizing mutual funds that invest in fixed-income securities.
